findings.title: Serve images that are appropriately-sized to save cellular data and improve load time
findings.description: Images should be served in appropriate sizes to reduce cellular data consumption and improve page loading times. Using formats like JPEG 2000, JPEG XR, and WebP can provide better compression than PNG or JPEG.

findings.title: Optimize Image Compression
findings.description: Using JPEG 2000, JPEG XR, and WebP image formats can provide better compression than PNG or JPEG, resulting in faster downloads and less data consumption.

findings.title: Server Response Time Optimization
findings.description: Keep the server response time for the main document short because all other requests depend on it.

findings.title: Potential dangers for remaining Roadmap targets
findings.description: CoinmarketCap and CoinGecko require high trading volume to achieve remaining Roadmap targets.
